 152:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) ErrorCallback                     : TIM Error Callback.
 153:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) CommutationCallback               : TIM Commutation Callback.
 154:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) CommutationHalfCpltCallback       : TIM Commutation half complete Callback.
 155:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim.c ****     (+) BreakCallback                     : TIM Break Callback.
